<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <header>
            <h1><%= title %></h1>
        </header>
        
        <main>
            <div class="welcome-section">
                <h2><%= message %></h2>
                <p>This is the foundation of your web application. The following features will be implemented:</p>
                
                <div class="features-list">
                    <div class="feature">
                        <h3>🔐 User Authentication</h3>
                        <p>Secure user registration and login system</p>
                        <span class="status pending">Coming Next</span>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="feature">
                        <h3>👤 Profile Management</h3>
                        <p>User profile CRUD operations</p>
                        <span class="status pending">Planned</span>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="feature">
                        <h3>📊 Dashboard</h3>
                        <p>User information display and navigation</p>
                        <span class="status pending">Planned</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="server-info">
                <h3>Server Status</h3>
                <p>✅ Express.js server is running</p>
                <p>✅ MVC architecture initialized</p>
                <p>✅ Session management configured</p>
            </div>
        </main>
        
        <footer>
            <p>Explorador Web Application - Task 1 Complete</p>
        </footer>
    </div>
    
    <script src="/js/main.js"></script>
</body>
</html>